_sText:
ATTENTION: Server Owners, make sure to delete any file titled bhop_bliss_v1.bsp , bhop_bliss.bsp before adding this map to your map pool. This map is the updated version of the first map.

I originally created this map almost 2 years ago or so, and I had inspiration from bhop_sQee. I understand that flat, ugly, simplistic textures arent very popular, however I really wanted to recreate this map because I didnt want to leave the original map in it's very low quality status.

Length: Medium/Long
Difficulty: Medium

I hope you enjoy the map, I love feedback.
And also, yes, I do plan on making maps that aren't ugly flat textures, just not right now.

Have fun!
